Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:43.62,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an2}Find  the  way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:44.83,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an2}Fly  Fafnir
